  <p class="ko" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">출처: 리처드 데니스·윌리엄 에크하르트의 1983년 터틀 트레이딩 실험(커티스 페이스, 『터틀 트레이딩』, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management"(SSRN 워킹페이퍼, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); 2020년 12월~2021년 4월 및 2023년 10~12월 비트코인 랠리, 2018년 및 2022년(테라·루나, FTX) 관련 가격 데이터.</p>
  <p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: Richard Dennis and William Eckhardt's 1983 Turtle Trading experiment (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (SSRN working paper, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); price data for Bitcoin's December 2020-April 2021 and October-December 2023 rallies, and its 2018 and 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX) declines.</p>
  <p class="ja" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">出典: リチャード・デニスとウィリアム・エックハートによる1983年のタートルトレーディング実験(カーティス・フェイス、『タートル流投資の魔術』、2007年); Nitish Poluri、"Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management"(SSRNワーキングペーパー、2026年、SSRN ID 6272239); 2020年12月~2021年4月および2023年10~12月のビットコインの上昇相場、2018年および2022年(テラ・ルナ、FTX)の下落に関する価格データ。</p>
  <p class="es" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fuentes: el experimento Turtle Trading de 1983 de Richard Dennis y William Eckhardt (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (working paper de SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); datos de precio de los rallies de Bitcoin de diciembre de 2020-abril de 2021 y octubre-diciembre de 2023, y de sus caídas de 2018 y 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX).</p>
  <p class="de" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Quellen: Richard Dennis' und William Eckhardts Turtle-Trading-Experiment von 1983 (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (SSRN-Working-Paper, 2026, SSRN-ID 6272239); Preisdaten zu Bitcoins Rallyes von Dezember 2020-April 2021 und Oktober-Dezember 2023 sowie seinen Rückgängen 2018 und 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX).</p>
  <p class="fr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources : l'expérience Turtle Trading de 1983 de Richard Dennis et William Eckhardt (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007) ; Nitish Poluri, « Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management » (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239) ; données de prix des rallyes du Bitcoin de décembre 2020-avril 2021 et octobre-décembre 2023, et de ses baisses de 2018 et 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX).</p>
  <p class="pt" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Fontes: o experimento Turtle Trading de 1983 de Richard Dennis e William Eckhardt (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (working paper do SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); dados de preço dos ralis do Bitcoin de dezembro de 2020-abril de 2021 e outubro-dezembro de 2023, e de suas quedas de 2018 e 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX).</p>
  <p class="tr" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Kaynaklar: Richard Dennis ve William Eckhardt'ın 1983 Turtle Trading deneyi (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (SSRN çalışma raporu, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); Bitcoin'in Aralık 2020-Nisan 2021 ve Ekim-Aralık 2023 rallileri ile 2018 ve 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX) düşüşlerine ilişkin fiyat verileri.</p>
  <p class="vi" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Nguồn: thí nghiệm Turtle Trading năm 1983 của Richard Dennis và William Eckhardt (Curtis Faith, Way of the Turtle, 2007); Nitish Poluri, "Evaluating the Performance of a Donchian Channel Breakout Strategy with ATR-Based Risk Management" (working paper SSRN, 2026, SSRN ID 6272239); dữ liệu giá về các đợt tăng giá Bitcoin tháng 12/2020-4/2021 và tháng 10-12/2023, và các đợt giảm giá năm 2018 và 2022 (Terra-Luna, FTX).</p>
